            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;The fastest way is the most obviously naive solution. I tested all of the proposed solutions for symmetric diff in this thread, and the winner is: &lt;code&gt;function diff2(a, b) {     var i,         la = a.length,         lb = b.length,         res = [];      if (!la) return b;     else if (!lb) return a;      for (i = 0; i &amp;lt; la; i++) {         if (b.indexOf(a[i]) === -1) res.push(a[i]);     }     for (i = 0; i &amp;lt; lb; i++) {         if (a.indexOf(b[i]) === -1) res.push(b[i]);     }     return res; }&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

